---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Bold gradient backdrop — Viktor-style but lightened so dark text still reads. -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
    <!-- Base wash: peach top → pink mid → lavender bottom -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffd5b8 0%, #ffc7d6 38%, #e0c8ff 72%, #d4d6ff 100%);"
    ></div>
    <!-- Warm spotlight in upper-center, mimics Viktor's bright focal area -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(70% 55% at 50% 12%, #ffe1bf 0%, rgba(255,225,191,0.55) 28%, rgba(255,225,191,0) 60%);"
    ></div>
    <!-- Lavender bloom from the right side -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(50% 60% at 90% 70%, rgba(190,168,255,0.55) 0%, rgba(190,168,255,0) 60%);"
    ></div>
    <!-- Bottom fade-out to off-white so the gradient stops before the products section -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-48"
      style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(250, 250, 247, 0), var(--color-paper) 100%);"
    ></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-10 pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20 md:pb-32">
  <h1 class="font-hero text-[56px] sm:text-[80px] md:text-[112px] lg:text-[136px] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.035em] font-medium">
    Three products.<br />
    <span class="text-[var(--color-brand)]">Built by the tool<br />we're building.</span>
  </h1>
  <div class="mt-10 md:mt-14 max-w-2xl text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.55] text-[var(--color-muted)]">
    <p>
      MOOOON is building three pieces of software — a task manager, an AI-team desktop runtime, and the
      project-management tool that plans them both. The third one isn't shipped yet. We're using its workflow to build
      the other two anyway. <a href="#how" class="text-[var(--color-ink)] link-underline">See how</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-16 md:mt-24 flex items-center gap-3 text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" class="animate-pulse">
      <path d="M10 4v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>
